The kind of implicit behavior that you describe is not currently possible, and would require the ability to tell Deno to "unref" the stream. The conventional approach is to be explicit — [exit](https://doc.deno.land/deno/stable/~/Deno.exit) your program when it is time to terminate:

```ts
Deno.exit();
```

